{"paging":{"is_end":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/comments/567202163/child_comments?include=%24%5B%2A%5D.author%2Creply_to_author%2Ccontent%2Cvote_count\u0026include=%24%5B%2A%5D.author%2Creply_to_author%2Ccontent%2Cvote_count\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=45\u0026tdsourcetag=s_pctim_aiomsg","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/comments/567202163/child_comments?include=%24%5B%2A%5D.author%2Creply_to_author%2Ccontent%2Cvote_count\u0026include=%24%5B%2A%5D.author%2Creply_to_author%2Ccontent%2Cvote_count\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=43\u0026tdsourcetag=s_pctim_aiomsg","totals":64},"data":[{"id":567766419,"type":"comment","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/comments/567766419","vote_count":0,"voting":false,"created_time":1546154835,"is_delete":false,"resource_type":"answer","content":"\u003cp\u003e我再强调一遍我的观点。关于如何理解集合的问题。我仅仅从逻辑上来讲，希望大家有一个客观心平气和的思考。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e公理集合论是目前代数的基石。当然你可以不从公理集合论出发，但是公理集合论目前是公认严谨的。希望大家能从逻辑上去想一想，我的提法有没有一点道理。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我们以 {a, b}这个集为例，这里a作为一个元素，到底代表什么东西。如果说a是一个东西，那么我们仅可从{a, b}中取出一个a，如果我们取出了两个a，那么这已经超出{a, b}的容量了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e好，接下来我们反过来说，集合规定只能有一个a，并且运算符通常可以取出两个或者更多个a，并且这样做是没有问题的。那么这里面会有两种可能性。第一，运算符本身是超越{a, b} 这个体系的。第二， a在这里不是一个，而是无限多个。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果运算符超越了{a, b}，那么结论如前述，运算符计算出来的最初结果原理上不会再属于{a, b}，但是碰巧可能是，或者可以映射回来。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果a表示的是无限多个，我们取出一个a'，这个a'实际上不是{a, b}中的a。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","author":{"role":"normal","member":{"id":"8e45364b3e363dc02e487c4ef94a64a1","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/people/8e45364b3e363dc02e487c4ef94a64a1","name":"basicquant","headline":"量化交易研究爱好者。","gender":1,"avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-79c71c1bc63ea507b398923f03b1fb08_s.jpg","type":"people","user_type":"people","badge":[],"is_following":false,"is_followed":false}},"is_author":false,"allow_like":true,"allow_delete":false,"replies_count":1,"can_recommend":false,"can_collapse":false,"reply_to_author":{"role":"normal","member":{"id":"d592d4c542152f9845f9f17dbdf5a2d5","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/people/d592d4c542152f9845f9f17dbdf5a2d5","name":"猹猹","headline":"声豚,玩梗,数据党,极值图论,实用主义","gender":1,"avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/87b9166eb163b859eb6894f4cf9efdd4_s.jpg","type":"people","user_type":"people","badge":[],"is_following":false,"is_followed":false}},"extra_info":{}}]}
